Package: DataDrivenSecFirehol
Type: Package
Title: Search a host IP to check wether it's been under any campaing (malware, botnet) and check where it matches.
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Pol S., Guillem G., Jeffrey M.
Maintainer: The package maintainer will be <solapol94@gmail.com>
Description: This package can be used in many enviroments where the analyst need more information about a given IP.
    Will allow you to query a huge amount the data withing seconds since all is collected/build at first to later on be able to query it.
